## 4. SCREEN FLOW (App Modes)

The app uses a `mode` state variable to switch between 5 screens:

```
landing (5s auto) → mode-select → lobby → game → summary
                                      ↑         │
                                      └─────────┘ (play again / new game)
```

| Mode | Screen | Description |
|------|--------|-------------|
| `landing` | Splash | Full-screen hero image, smoke animations, progress bar. Auto-goes to mode-select after 5s |
| `mode-select` | Choose play type | Offline vs Online cards. Shows animated role icons. Player rules box |
| `lobby` | Setup | Add/remove players, room options, role toggles, game settings, theme toggle |
| `game` | Active play | Flip cards, night sequence, day voting, abilities, event log |
| `summary` | End screen | Reveals all roles, event history, localStorage history, play again |

