## 6. ROLES & RULES

| Role | Team | Ability | Min players to include |
|------|------|---------|------------------------|
| Mafia | Mafia | Kill one player each night | Always (1–2 based on count) |
| Godfather | Mafia | Immune to Detective; leads Mafia | 6+ (optional toggle) |
| Grandmother | Civilian | If killed, takes one random Mafia with her | 6+ (optional toggle) |
| Civilian | Civilian | Vote out Mafia during day | Fills remaining slots |
| Doctor | Civilian | Save one player from death each night; cannot save same person twice in a row | 4+ |
| Detective | Civilian | Investigate one player; gets private "suspicious/not suspicious" result | 5+ |
| Spy | Civilian | Appears suspicious to Detective; wins with civilians; Mafia doesn't know them | 6+ (settings toggle) |
| Mayor | Civilian | Vote counts double; revealed when killed | 5+ (settings toggle) |
| Sniper | Civilian | One shot per game; dies if shoots innocent | 6+ (settings toggle) |
| Serial Killer | Neutral | Kills one each night; wins if last one standing | 7+ (settings toggle) |

### Mafia count by player count
- 4 players: 1 Mafia
- 5+ players: 2 Mafia

### Minimum players to start: **4**

### Win conditions
- **Civilians win:** All Mafia (Mafia + Godfather) eliminated
- **Mafia win:** Mafia count ≥ non-Mafia alive count
- **Serial Killer wins:** Only Serial Killer left alive

### Detective investigation rules
- Mafia, Spy, Serial Killer → "suspicious"
- Godfather → always "not suspicious" (immune)
- Everyone else → "not suspicious"

