## 12. WHAT IS NOT BUILT YET (Gaps for AI to know)

1. **No real online multiplayer** — "Online" mode only generates a share URL; other players cannot actually join or sync state
2. **No URL param handling** — `?room=...&code=...` in share link is not read on load
3. **No backend** — No API, database, or WebSocket server
4. **Host-only UX** — One device runs everything; players pass phone to see their card
5. **Missing image files** — Card back and Detective PNGs will cause build errors
6. **Missing index.html** — Vite entry HTML may need to be recreated
7. **No tests** — Zero unit or E2E tests
8. **Sniper uses `prompt()`** — Crude UX for target selection
9. **No role-specific player views** — Everyone sees the host screen

